ktik melindungi situs judol oleh beberapa pegawai Komdigi.</font></p><p tts-paragraph-index="6" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 2rem; position: relative; max-width: 100%; font-family: " atkinson="" hyperlegible",="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="tts-paragraph-player" style="visibility: hidden; opacity: 0; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: -5rem; width: 5rem; display: flex; flex-flow: column wrap; overflow: hidden; height: max(2.4rem, 100%); flex: 0 0 auto; gap: 1rem; max-width: 100%;"><span class="tts-circle" style="border-color: rgba(124, 145, 255, 0.4); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-radius: 1000px; position: absolute; width: 2.25rem; left: 0px; top: 0px; display: inline-block; height: 2.25rem; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%;"></span><span class="tts-paragraph-player-button tts-play-icon" title="Play/Pause" style="mask-position: left center; mask-repeat: no-repeat; position: relative; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; width: 2rem; height: 1rem; left: 0.6875rem; top: 0.6875rem; mask-image: url(" data:image="" svg+xml,%3csvg="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 24 24" %3e%3cpath="" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 5.653c0-1.502 1.61-2.455 2.927-1.73l11.54 6.347c1.365.75 1.365 2.71 0 3.46l-11.54 6.348C6.61 20.802 5 19.85 5 18.348V5.652Zm2.108-.241a.275.275 0 0 0-.408.24v12.695c0 .21.224.342.408.241l11.54-6.347a.275.275 0 0 0 0-.482L7.108 5.412Z" clip-rule="evenodd" %3e%3c="" svg%3e");="" max-width:="" 100%;"=""></span></span><font color="#000000">âDan dia tidak tahu sama sekali. Dia tidak tahu sama sekali. Jadi kita jalankan ini, dia tidak tahu sama sekali. Saya bisa pertanggungjawabkan, dunia akhirat. Itu saja,â tegas dia.</font></p><p tts-paragraph-index="7" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 2rem; position: relative; max-width: 100%; font-family: " atkinson="" hyperlegible",="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="tts-paragraph-player" style="visibility: hidden; opacity: 0; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: -5rem; width: 5rem; display: flex; flex-flow: column wrap; overflow: hidden; height: max(2.4rem, 100%); flex: 0 0 auto; gap: 1rem; max-width: 100%;"><span class="tts-circle" style="border-color: rgba(124, 145, 255, 0.4); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-image: none 100% / 1 / 0 stretch; border-radius: 1000px; position: absolute; width: 2.25rem; left: 0px; top: 0px; display: inline-block; height: 2.25rem; cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%;"></span><span class="tts-paragraph-player-button tts-play-icon" title="Play/Pause" style="mask-position: left center; mask-repeat: no-repeat; position: relative; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; width: 2rem; height: 1rem; left: 0.6875rem; top: 0.6875rem; mask-image: url(" data:image="" svg+xml,%3csvg="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 24 24" %3e%3cpath="" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 5.653c0-1.502 1.61-2.455 2.927-1.73l11.54 6.347c1.365.75 1.365 2.71 0 3.46l-11.54 6.348C6.61 20.802 5 19.85 5 18.348V5.652Zm2.108-.241a.275.275 0 0 0-.408.24v12.695c0 .21.224.342.408.241l11.54-6.347a.275.275 0 0 0 0-.482L7.108 5.412Z" clip-rule="evenodd" %3e%3c="" svg%3e");="" max-width:="" 100%;"=""></span></span><font color="#000000">Sebelumnya, Zulkarnaen Apriliantony, Adhi Kismanto, Alwin Jabarti Kiemas, dan Muhrijan terlibat dalam aksi melindungi sejumlah situs judi&nbsp;<em style="max-width: 100%;">online&nbsp;</em>(judol) agar tidak diblokir Kementerian Komunikasi dan Informatika (Kominfo), kini Kementerian Komunikasi dan Digital (Komdigi).</font></p><p tts-paragraph-index="8" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 2rem; position: relative; max-width: 100%; font-family: " atkinson="" hyperlegible",="" sans-serif;"=""><span class="tts-paragraph-player" style="visibility: hidden; opacity: 0; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: -5rem; width: 5rem; display: flex; flex-flow: column wrap; overflow: hidden; height: max(2.4rem, 100%); flex: 0 0 auto; gap: 1rem; max-widt